like this living process takes place, you

165
00:34:27,290 --> 00:34:28,970
become your Spirit.

166
00:34:28,970 --> 00:34:36,550
We never think this thing is around us, every 
day we see.

167
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:38,820
This is worked out by this all pervading Power.

168
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:43,060
