169
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:47,560
We cannot transform even one flower into a 
fruit.

170
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,590
We take it for granted.

171
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:52,760
We never know that all such living things 
are done.

172
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:53,760
Now look at it.

173
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:57,560
There is a little bird, which lays the egg.

174
00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:58,630
For what?

175
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:02,250
The eggs are kept in the nest.

176
00:35:02,250 --> 00:35:10,270
The all pervading Power works it out in such 
a way that the eggs grow and the bird hatches

177
00:35:10,270 --> 00:35:17,020
them and from these eggs comes out a bird.

178
00:35:17,020 --> 00:35:20,870
We have seen caterpillars turning into butterflies.

179
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:23,250
We never think how it happens.

180
00:35:23,250 --> 00:35:25,620
We just take it for granted.

181
00:35:25,620 --> 00:35:27,200
We enjoy their colors.

182
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:34,940
We never see how this transformation has taken 
place and this transmutation has taken place.

183
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:41,870
