00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:57,200
The Kundalini has to move throughout the centers 
and you have to feel the actualization of

188
00:35:57,200 --> 00:36:02,380
your Realization, meaning that you must feel 
the cool breeze coming out of your fontanelle

189
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:03,760
bone area.

190
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,670
Realization you have to feel.

191
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:10,620
It’s an actualization, not a vague belief, 
I told them hundred times.

192
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:13,620
