fall of Dharma, fall of your values, your

691
01:13:25,350 --> 01:13:33,910
virtues, whenever the saints suffer, I come 
on this Earth to save the Saints and kill

692
01:13:33,910 --> 01:13:35,170
the devils."

693
01:13:35,170 --> 01:13:38,880
But the devils have gone into the Saints now.

694
01:13:38,880 --> 01:13:41,780
It’s a problem, a dilemma for me.

695
01:13:41,780 --> 01:13:42,780
What to do.

696
01:13:42,780 --> 01:13:45,320
These devils have come into your brains.

697
01:13:45,320 --> 01:13:47,840
They are to be taken out, first of all.

698
01:13:47,840 --> 01:13:50,630
Just wait for me to finish.

699
01:13:50,630 --> 01:13:52,500
Do not stick on to one question.

700
01:13:52,500 --> 01:13:55,260
If you stick on, you’ll miss the whole point.

701
01:13:55,260 --> 01:13:57,220
By questioning, you will not get Realization.

702
01:13:57,220 --> 01:13:59,890
It’s not a mental activity.

703
01:13:59,890 --> 01:14:03,080
It’s triggering beyond the mental activity.

704
01:14:03,080 --> 01:14:07,250
This lecture is useless if you do not get 
your Realization.

705
01:14:07,250 --> 01:14:11,260
In the beginning of the Vedas it was written 
that if you do not get the knowledge… Knowledge

706
01:14:11,260 --> 01:14:12,570
doesn’t mean going mad.

707
01:14:12,570 --> 01:14:15,180
It doesn’t mean hypnosis.

708
01:14:15,180 --> 01:14:18,990
But if you do not feel the all pervading Power, 
then these Vedas are useless.

709
01:14:18,990 --> 01:14:24,610
In the same way my lecture and all mental 
activities are useless if you do not get your

710
01:14:24,610 --> 01:14:25,610
Realization.

711
01:14:25,610 --> 01:14:27,890
That’s the main thing you must have.

712
01:14:27,890 --> 01:14:34,760
May God bless you.

713
01:14:34,760 --> 01:14:43,360
Now, ask me a question.

714
01:14:43,360 --> 01:14:49,450
Seeker: What is the best approach we can take 
to go to Laxmi?

715
01:14:49,450 --> 01:14:54,410
Shri Mataji: I will tell you tomorrow about 
Laxmi, where she is settled down.

716
01:14:54,410 --> 01:14:57,540
That’s what we are going to do, all the 
Goddess, not one.

717
01:14:57,540 --> 01:14:59,580
All in one bundle.

718
01:14:59,580 --> 01:15:07,140
Now what do you say to that?

719
01:15:07,140 --> 01:15:14,050
Alright, good idea.

720
01:15:14,050 --> 01:15:24,810
Seeker: Asks about how to deal with her worries.

721
01:15:24,810 --> 01:15:25,820
Alright, doesn’t matter.

722
01:15:25,820 --> 01:15:30,250
We are going to work it out.

723
01:15:30,250 --> 01:15:32,590
Don’t worry about your personal things.

724
01:15:32,590 --> 01:15:45,740
It’s all 
going to work out en masse.

725
01:15:45,740 --> 01:15:47,940
Dr.

726
01:15:47,940 --> 01:15:52,830
Warren: She is asking whether you said to 
say, “Mother, I am not guilty”.

727
01:15:52,830 --> 01:15:55,900
Shri Mataji: Yes, yes, please, within yourself.

728
01:15:55,900 --> 01:15:56,900
Very important.

729
01:15:56,900 --> 01:15:57,900
What is it?

730
01:15:57,900 --> 01:15:58,900
Dr.

731
01:15:58,900 --> 01:15:59,900
Warren:She is liking it!

732
01:15:59,900 --> 01:16:01,450
Shri Mataji: Good, good.

733
01:16:01,450 --> 01:16:03,150
May God bless you.

734
01:16:03,150 --> 01:16:05,260
Don’t feel guilty at all.

735
01:16:05,260 --> 01:16:07,550
Otherwise I would not come here.

736
01:16:07,550 --> 01:16:14,770
The ones who have harmed you are guilty.

737
01:16:14,770 --> 01:16:32,230
Seeker: What is your capacity and our capacity 
to hate the devils.

738
01:16:32,230 --> 01:16:34,710
Most religions preached that we should not 
be angry.

739
01:16:34,710 --> 01:16:40,300
Shri Mataji: You should not be angry, but 
with Devils?

740
01:16:40,300 --> 01:16:44,930
You run away from them.

741
01:16:44,930 --> 01:16:45,930
Let me handle them.

742
01:16:45,930 --> 01:16:46,930
You just don’t worry about them.

743
01:16:46,930 --> 01:16:47,930
It’s my job.

744
01:16:47,930 --> 01:17:07,480
First of all you love yourself, have self-esteem, 
know that you are the temple of God, Then

745
01:17:07,480 --> 01:17:11,880
you love by becoming realized, you become 
collectively conscious.

746
01:17:11,880 --> 01:17:13,790
Again the word becoming.

747
01:17:13,790 --> 01:17:16,170
Then you start feeling the other within yourself.

748
01:17:16,170 --> 01:17:17,170
Who is the other?

749
01:17:17,170 --> 01:17:20,390
I am not helping you, you are part and parcel 
of my being.

750
01:17:20,390 --> 01:17:25,130
If I am helping my finger, am I helping you?

751
01:17:25,130 --> 01:17:33,140
Then we see about the rest of the thing.

752
01:17:33,140 --> 01:17:50,710
You don’t worry about them.

753
01:17:50,710 --> 01:18:00,130
Seeker: Many of the people who come to my 
clinic have activated their Kundalini too

754
01:18:00,130 --> 01:18:02,780
early and I’m wondering how to help them.

755
01:18:02,780 --> 01:18:12,480
Shri Mataji: They do not activate their Kundalini, 
they do not.

756
01:18:12,480 --> 01:18:16,070
All these things are just to activate the 
sympathetic and it’s very dangerous.

757
01:18:16,070 --> 01:18:20,660
You can get blisters, you can get all kinds 
of problems.

758
01:18:20,660 --> 01:18:24,310
You can get cancer also.

759
01:18:24,310 --> 01:18:26,200
I get so many people like that.

760
01:18:26,200 --> 01:18:29,490
I’ll make you the masters.

761
01:18:29,490 --> 01:18:31,740
It’s Love.

762
01:18:31,740 --> 01:18:32,900
It cannot harm.

763
01:18:32,900 --> 01:18:34,500
It’s your Mother.

764
01:18:34,500 --> 01:18:39,420
That’s the only Mother you have and you 
are the only child.

765
01:18:39,420 --> 01:18:41,730
How can your Kundalini trouble you?

766
01:18:41,730 --> 01:18:46,150
She is just waiting for the moment to give 
you realization.

767
01:18:46,150 --> 01:18:57,320
She loves you the most of all.

768
01:18:57,320 --> 01:19:05,380
And you cannot activate it, it just spontaneously 
rises.

769
01:19:05,380 --> 01:19:08,780
I was myself amazed to read some books on 
Kundalini.

770
01:19:08,780 --> 01:19:12,060
I said these people don’t know what Kundalini 
is.

771
01:19:12,060 --> 01:19:13,360
They’re liars.

772
01:19:13,360 --> 01:19:20,270
They are cheats writing such big books about 
Kundalini without knowing a word, without

773
01:19:20,270 --> 01:19:21,480
having any authority.

774
01:19:21,480 --> 01:19:23,550
You have to have Divine Authority, isn’t 
it?

775
01:19:23,550 --> 01:19:27,220
You cannot get it in a Theological college 
or any place you go to.

776
01:19:27,220 --> 01:19:34,960
Its a Divine Authority you must have.

777
01:19:34,960 --> 01:19:38,310
Seeker: Should we love our enemies as well?

778
01:19:38,310 --> 01:19:43,220
Shri Mataji: First of all you love yourself 
and your friends.

779
01:19:43,220 --> 01:19:51,500
Then we can talk of enemies.

780
01:19:51,500 --> 01:19:53,780
You have to know who are your enemies.

781
01:19:53,780 --> 01:19:57,490
Actually, you don’t know who are your enemies.

782
01:19:57,490 --> 01:20:03,790
First, we have to develop that discretion 
power.

783
01:20:03,790 --> 01:20:07,820
By your vibrations you will know who is who, 
because once you are connected with the mains,

784
01:20:07,820 --> 01:20:09,680
you start feeling it.

785
01:20:09,680 --> 01:20:15,680
You can ask any question whichever is an absolute 
question.

786
01:20:15,680 --> 01:20:17,300
You can ask is there God?

787
01:20:17,300 --> 01:20:19,440
You will start feeling a cool breeze coming 
in.

788
01:20:19,440 --> 01:20:23,930
Like a computer, you become connected with 
the mains and you answer all these questions.

789
01:20:23,930 --> 01:20:32,310
You develop your discretion and you will know 
who are yours and who are not yours.

790
01:20:32,310 --> 01:20:39,910
Before that you don’t know, you are so mixed 
up.

791
01:20:39,910 --> 01:20:49,970
Actually there are very few enemies that you 
have, very few.

792
01:20:49,970 --> 01:20:52,680
Should we now have it?

793
01:20:52,680 --> 01:20:57,780
You’ve got that door open there.

794
01:20:57,780 --> 01:21:04,470
Just get one of the doors open for some of 
the enemies to fly out.

795
01:21:04,470 --> 01:21:07,960
Dr.

796
01:21:07,960 --> 01:21:16,280
Warren: If anyone has their shoes on, take 
them off and simply put your hands out towards

797
01:21:16,280 --> 01:21:23,340
Mataji as if asking for it.

798
01:21:23,340 --> 01:21:24,490
Be humble about it.

799
01:21:24,490 --> 01:21:25,490
Be open-minded.

800
01:21:25,490 --> 01:21:28,230
If you’ve got a lot of questions…

801
01:21:28,230 --> 01:21:29,900
Shri Mataji: Sit comfortably.

802
01:21:29,900 --> 01:21:32,320
There is nothing to put yourself to stay.

803
01:21:32,320 --> 01:21:37,130
Your neck should be bending neither forward 
nor backward.

804
01:21:37,130 --> 01:21:39,430
There is no effort to be put in.

805
01:21:39,430 --> 01:21:40,430
Just sit comfortably.

806
01:21:40,430 --> 01:21:43,430
Kundalini will rise by itself and you’ll 
get your Realization.

807
01:21:43,430 --> 01:21:45,470
You don’t have to do anything.

808
01:21:45,470 --> 01:21:48,880
Just don’t put your concentration onto one 
point.

809
01:21:48,880 --> 01:21:51,670
Some people have a habit of concentrating 
here, concentrating there.

810
01:21:51,670 --> 01:21:56,590
All those people who have done this concentration 
business or, what is that the another one,

811
01:21:56,590 --> 01:22:00,210
putting the tongue back?

812
01:22:00,210 --> 01:22:03,630
(kechari mudra).

813
01:22:03,630 --> 01:22:12,140
Whatever you have done, all such people should 
put their attention here (top of head).

814
01:22:12,140 --> 01:22:13,690
There is the door, not here.

815
01:22:13,690 --> 01:22:14,710
That’s all.

816
01:22:14,710 --> 01:22:24,000
But rest of the people just keep your attention 
absolutely loose.

817
01:22:24,000 --> 01:22:31,010
Now, close your eyes.

818
01:22:31,010 --> 01:22:35,360
Keep your eyes closed, because Kundalini has 
to pass through Agnya chakra and if your eyes

819
01:22:35,360 --> 01:22:40,290
are not closed, she won’t rise.

820
01:22:40,290 --> 01:22:43,010
Put your hands towards me just like this.

821
01:22:43,010 --> 01:22:48,490
All of you, please put your hands, because 
in the hands you have those centers.

822
01:22:48,490 --> 01:22:51,760
I would request you to take out if there is 
anything heavy in your necks.

823
01:22:51,760 --> 01:22:53,000
Please, take off.

824
01:22:53,000 --> 01:22:54,240
It is better.

825
01:22:54,240 --> 01:22:58,580
Also, if there is anything heavy or tight 
on your waist.

826
01:22:58,580 --> 01:23:09,050
You can loosen your belt a little bit.

827
01:23:09,050 --> 01:23:27,600
Just put your hands towards me.

828
01:23:27,600 --> 01:23:36,880
Close your eyes.

829
01:23:49,300 --> 01:24:02,160
Please, put your right hand on your heart, 
because Spirit resides in our heart.

830
01:24:02,260 --> 01:24:06,840
Sit very comfortably without any strain on 
your back.

831
01:24:06,840 --> 01:24:08,320
That is very important.

832
01:24:17,700 --> 01:24:35,020
First of all, you have to ask in your heart, 
“Mother, am I the Spirit?” Not dead spirit but Atma.
